        "description": "Beam diameter range for industrial cleaning; smaller (100-200 μm) for fine detail on shale surfaces, larger (300-500 μm) for broad area prep. Recommended 200 μm for uniform energy distribution on irregular shale textures. Source: Equipment specifications (e.g., Coherent Armoni series) and process optimization for stone cleaning."
